author: sviens
msg: Updated comments related to mark this artifact as containing UDDI v3 functionality.

author: sviens
msg: When only the "sortByNameAsc" find qualifier is specified, BusinessList, ServiceList and TModelList were not returned in the correctly sorted order (ascending by name).  See JIRA issue JUDDI-50 for more information (http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JUDDI-50)

author: sviens
msg: Commented out marshalling/unmarshalling of CategoryBag for BindingTemplate.  BindingTemplate should not contain a CategoryBag until jUDDI is ready to support UDDI v3.

author: sviens
msg: The fetchBusiness method should not add empty CategoryBag or IdentifierBag to the returned Business.  The fetchBusiness method now checks to be sure there's something in each bag before adding it to the business.  The fetchService method had a similar issue with empty CategoryBag.  See JIRA issue JUDDI-43 for more information (http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JUDDI-43)

author: sviens
msg: The BusinessKey used in the search was not being returned in the RelatedBusinessList response as it should have been.  See JIRA issue JUDDI-42 for more information (http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JUDDI-42)
